title: Street Lights
subTitle: James, a highly efficient police officer, sets out to unveil the mystery behind a burglary that shook everyone in the city. He meets several people to solve the crime and put the thieves behind bars.

title: Hotel California
subTitle: Jimmy, a petty thief, is tasked with smuggling the print of an unreleased film out of the city. His journey, however, is peppered with several confusing situations.

title: Minnaminnikkoottam
subTitle: Ajit, an anchor in Kolkata, meets Krishnapriya, who has lost her husband under mysterious circumstances. However, things become complicated when he falls for her while helping to find her spouse.

title: Kili Poyi
subTitle: Friends Chacko and Hari are fed up with their employer and plan a trip to Goa. Their trip turns into something unusual when they discover a mysterious bag.

title: Casanova
subTitle: A group of masked fugitives kill the girlfriend of an international businessman, Casanovva. In order to avenge her death and capture the culprits, Casanovva sets up a fake television reality show.

title: Moz & Cat
subTitle: Two orphans cause mischief to earn their daily bread, but their lives change when a woman seeks their help to save her brother.

title: Ennum Eppozhum
subTitle: Vineeth, a magazine reporter, lacks the inspiration to work hard. However, his life takes a turn when he is asked to interview a family court lawyer.

title: 3 Dots
subTitle: Three ex-convicts, Vishnu, Pappan, and Louis, want to reform themselves by taking help from Dr Isaac, the prison counsellor. However, Dr Isaac has different intentions which will land them in trouble.

title: Bahubali-2
subTitle: After learning that his father was brutally killed by Bhallaladeva, Mahendra Baahubali raises an army to defeat him and release his mother from the former's captivity.

title: Vinodayathra
subTitle: Vinod, a quarrelsome young man, moves into his sister's house in a village to get his life in order. There, he happens to meet Anupama and falls in love with her.

title: Vinodayathra

title: Junior Senior
subTitle: Two friends, Santosh and Shakti, fall in love with the same woman. When the woman chooses Santosh due to his financial status, the latter decides to call off their relationship.

title: Olu
subTitle: A girl's spirit connects with a struggling painter, infusing his art with divine inspiration. Their love transcends earthly boundaries yet faces a perilous test when worldly temptations beckon.

title: Pigman
subTitle: After his thesis gets rejected and he gets expelled from his college, the idealistic Sreekumar is left with no choice but to take up menial jobs in a pigsty.

title: Sherlock Toms
subTitle: Inspired by Sherlock Holmes, an IRS officer, resolves to employ his analytical prowess in tackling an extensive criminal operation.

title: Evidam Swargamanu
subTitle: Mathews owns a farm that is the envy of everyone in the village. It attracts the attention of a dirty land dealer, who entangles him in a vicious bureaucratic web to take it away from him.

title: Karyasthan
subTitle: After a past incident, two powerful clans of Krishnapuram remain estranged until one day, a man with a mysterious past decides to bring the families together.

title: Ranam
subTitle: Chinna moves to the city for his studies but gets into an altercation with Bhagawati's gang. Subsequently, his life takes a turn for the worse when he falls for Maheswari, Bhagawati's sister.

title: Manjummel Boys
subTitle: After one of them falls inside a dangerous pit in the Guna Caves, a group of childhood friends muster courage to rescue him out of a space from where a return is next to impossible.

title: Robinhood
subTitle: A thief robs the automated teller machines of the Imperial Bank of India. Worried about the safety of the bank, the managing director decides to hire a private detective to solve the case.

title: Robinhood

title: Kadha, Samvidhanam Kunchakko
subTitle: Kunchacko, a millionaire who built his fortune through questionable means, marries Mary and vows to change. However, leaving his past behind proves to be harder than he imagined.

title: Al Mallu
subTitle: After being cheated on by her prospective groom, Nayana learns that he also cheated on one of her close friends too. Thus, she decides to teach him a lesson.

title: God's Own Country
subTitle: The lives of a taxi driver, a man travelling to Kerala and a public prosecutor intertwine with each other as they seek monetary aid and justice.

title: Ring Master
subTitle: Prince, a dog trainer, faces an awkward situation when his pet dog Diana acts in a film alongside his former lover, an actress who shares the same name as the dog.

title: Vishwaroopam 2
subTitle: Wisam Ahmad Kashmiri, a RAW agent, tries to prevent a terrorist organisation from executing a deadly mission against three countries.

title: Aadu 2
subTitle: Shaji Pappan and his team participate in a tug-of-war tournament to overcome their financial crisis. However, fate entangles them in a counterfeiting deal.

title: Kammatti Paadam
subTitle: Krishnan returns home to Kammattippaadam after a call from his friend Ganga. Together, they face their dark past as old crimes resurface, putting their lives in danger.

title: King of Kotha
subTitle: Heartbroken on being back-stabbed by his childhood friend, Raju, an influential man, runs away from his hometown, Kotha. Soon, to bring back order in the town, a police officer plots a plan.

title: Vikrithi
subTitle: After spending two sleepless nights taking care of his sick daughter, a person with hearing and speech disability falls asleep in a metro. A passenger photographs him and shares it online.
